To address the layout issues in the "Add Item" screen and ensure a seamless, gap-free interface, I will restructure the modal in `pages/DailyTransactions.tsx`.

The new structure separates the **Top App Bar** (Fixed) from the **Scrollable Content**. Inside the scrollable area, I will place a **Sticky Header** containing the Search Bar and Filter Chips. This ensures the search bar sits immediately below the app bar with zero whitespace, and remains sticky while scrolling the list.

